APPEALS ALLOWED

01-1165. Frenchtown Square Partnership v. Lemstone, Inc.

Mahoning App. No. 99CA300, The appeal is allowed on Proposition of Law No. I.

Douglas and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Moyer, C. J., and Lundberg Stratton, J., would allow all propositions of law. Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Cook, JJ., dissent.
